strings: <voice_0x01001628><se_def>Rhapthorne: Pitiful humans! Even after so many failed attempts to stop me, you still labour in the hope that you can come between me and my destiny!

<voice_0x01001629><se_def>Rhapthorne: But your hope is trickling away.
Soon it will be gone, leaving only despair.
<voice_0x0100162A><se_def>Rhapthorne: And the further you fall into its black depths, the stronger my flesh and blood shall become!

<voice_0x01001627><se_def>Rhapthorne: You will revere me!
And you will offer up your pitiful lives as
a mark of your respect and adoration!
